org.apache.hadoop.fs

Class TestFileUtil.MyFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.File
      • org.apache.hadoop.fs.TestFileUtil.MyFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<File>
    Enclosing class:
    TestFileUtil

    public static class TestFileUtil.MyFile
extends File
    Extend File. Same as File except for two things: (1) This treats file1Name as a very special file which is not delete-able irrespective of it's parent-dir's permissions, a peculiar file instance for testing. (2) It returns the files in alphabetically sorted order when listed.
